The terms have been updated to reflect the revised structure from the issue 
  comments. Here's a summary of the changes made:                             
                                                                              
  **Original (incorrect):** Added only 2 flat terms as children of            
  EFO_0022606.                                                                
                                                                              
  **Updated (correct):** 4 terms implementing the versioned hierarchy         
  requested in the issue comments:                                            
                                                                              
   ID           | Label                       | Parent      | Synonym         
  --------------|-----------------------------|-------------|---------------  
   EFO_0920086  | 10x gene expression flex v1 | EFO_0022606 | —               
   EFO_0920087  | 10x Next GEM Flex v1        | EFO_0920086 | Next GEM Flex   
   EFO_0920088  | 10x GEM-X Flex v1           | EFO_0920086 | GEM-X Flex      
   EFO_0920089  | 10x GEM-X Flex v2           | EFO_0022606 | —               
                                                                              
  The update accounts for the new GEM-X Flex v2 released in December 2025,    
  which uses a different plate-based multiplexing system (10bp barcodes, up to
  384 samples/week) rather than the microfluidic chip approach of v1.

